narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I enjoyed the schedule of diverse speakers. I heard different methodological approaches that I plan on using in my own research.
I learned about the functioning of the US political system. Very interesting

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The strengths are seeing others within the field engaging with difficult questions. The worst part of the course is when some people make their questions/responses more focused on their own research than on the presentation.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I think the AP workshop has conclusions that students and faculty from all fields can learn from.
Yes, it is a great forum for learning
